>

<MethodEndpoint
  method={"get"}
  path={"/receiver/data/v1/credit-fixed-incomes/investments/{consentPactualId}/{investmentId}"}
  context={"endpoint"}
>
  
</MethodEndpoint>



Endpoint that our client must call to get the information from Open Finance:
    
* Open Finance endpoint that will be requested: ```(GET /investments/{investmentId})```
    
* FamilyType: ```Investimentos - Renda Fixa Crédito``` 
    
The response content provided by this endpoint uses the same entity as the provided on the [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/360775958/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DC+Renda+Fixa+Cr+dito-+v1.0.2).
